Choose the best USPS delivery option based on price, package size, weight and delivery date.



Always get the lowest rates with the fastest delivery times.


Choose the best USPS delivery option based on price, package size, weight and delivery date.

USPS has a lot of great ways to ship stuff — we support them all. But deciding which one is best for each package can be tough. Not anymore. Stamps.com automatically selects the best USPS delivery option based on price, package size, weight and required delivery date. And of course, with the fastest delivery and lowest rates, Stamps.com will also help boost your seller ratings.
USPS has a lot of great ways to ship your stuff – we support them all. But deciding which one is the best for each package can be tough. Stamps.com displays all USPS delivery options with rates and estimated delivery times, allowing you to easily choose the most cost-effective option for your package.





The right fit no matter how much you ship.


From one package a week from your home to multiple packages every day from several warehouses.

Whether you ship one package a day from your home, or ship thousands of packages a day from multiple warehouses, Stamps.com works for any-sized business and any experience level. Our easy-to-use interface doesn’t require any special training or special equipment — any computer and printer will do. Just give us a try and we guarantee you’ll be shipping within minutes.














