The easy way to ship international…
				We fill out the customs forms for you!


Imports order data from Amazon, eBay, Etsy, and more




One of the fastest ways to grow your business is to open up to international markets. It’s easy with Stamps.com. Stamps.com automatically fills out the custom forms with the delivery address, product descriptions and number of units imported from your marketplace or store. Everything you need is built right into the software. All the forms. All the best prices.
One of the fastest ways to grow your business is to open up to international markets. It’s easy with Stamps.com — with integrated Custom Forms, we insert the delivery address directly into the form. Stamps.com also includes the date, your name and the USPS Electronic Round Stamp. Everything you need is built right into the software. All the forms. All the best prices.




